node.text: No more Zoom for my fight camps, my friends! That's 2020. We're going VR now. I just joined @zuck and @boztank to try out Horizon Workrooms. It feels like you're in the same room. It's ridiculous. It's a new virtual collab app for Oculus and it's the future. See you in the metaverse 🤙
